Invocation Name: res guide
des: You can as the Medical Residency guide for information on any medical specialty. Information includes statistics like the match rate, average income, number of publications, and step score of every specialty. You can ask about any field, such as dermatology, radiation oncology, family medicine, and many more.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
